events.description: We turn the cube and it twists us! Compete in solving the 3x3 and 4x4 Cubes with other masters of Cube.
events.name: Rubik's Cube
events.prize-worth: The Cube themselves will be given as prizes.
rules: Time limit for solving 3x3x3 is 5 minutes
Time limit for solving 4x4x4 is 10 minutes
Cube should not be damaged, marked or otherwise altered.
If for any reason cube doesn't function correctly  falls apart or moves out of the solved state accidentally once the timer has stopped the cube will be considered as unsolved.
Competitor must place their hands flat on table and must not have any physical contact with the cube before the starting of game.
In any case of cheating or not abiding by the rules, there will be a penalty of 15s
You will only be given one chance.
For 3x3x3 cubes winners will be decided on the basis of time taken to solve the cube
For 4x4x4 winners will be decided on the basis of total no. of faces solved in minimum time.

events.description: It is a multiplayer first person shooter game played between counter terrorists and terrorists. It shall comprise of knockout rounds to semis to finals.
events.name: Counter Strike: Global Offensive
rules: Server settings will be as per standard rules of Competitive Match-Making.
In case of Tie, overtime of 6 rounds will be used to decide the winner.
The map pool will always be the Active Duty map pool and therefore might be updated before each tournament: de_nuke, de_cache, de_train, de_mirage, de_inferno, de_overpass, de_cbble
A knife round will be played to determine the side. This is forced by the server. The winner of this knife round will choose the side by typing .stay or . switch in the chat.
If the server crashes at any given time, the existing score will be retained and the match will be reset.
All teams are expected to be there and confirm their attendance 15 minutes before the start of the match.
Foul language, offensive and disruptive behaviour will not be tolerated from any player and will result in the loss of the match thereby dropping out of tournament.
All participants must adhere to the decisions and rules of the tournament organisers, admins, and referees. All decisions are final, except in cases where the option to appeal is clearly stated.

events.description: The best players in the area come together ! Do you have what it takes to be the best? Compete and show everyone what it takes to become a REAL CHAMPION!
events.name: FIFA-15
rules: Players shall not receive coaching during a tournament match. Communications of any kind, audible or visible, between a player and a coach may be construed as coaching.
Players are not allowed to plug any devices, other than controllers, into any console. All the required things will be provided by the organisers.

Competitors may provide their own controller so long as the controller does not provide an unfair competitive advantage to the competitor, does not interfere with the operations of the game or tournament, does not require any special configuration, cabling or adapters to function and is designed to work natively on the console the competitor competes on. The organisers may, at its sole discretion, disallow any controller and require the competitor to use an approved controller.
Each Player will have 2-3 minutes to configure controls, adjust line-ups and settings in accordance with the rules.
Players not present at the designated start time for any match will be disqualified, and their opponent shall be granted a 3-0 score.

Each Player can pause the game up to five times. If a Player pauses the game, it must be to make a tactical change to their squad, which can include substitutions, formation changes, or tactic adjustments.
All the matches will be of 1v1 type.

events.description: Calling all motor heads. If you're the sort of chap who lives life in the fast lane, then the world of NFS:MW would be very familiar domain. A cult classic, this game has gone down in the books as one of the best racing games ever made.

rules: The tournament will be knock out.
The player who wins their 1st stage match advances to the next stage.
There will not be any match played for the third spot.
Race Mode Options: * Nitrous: On * Collision Detection: oN * Performance Matching: Off * Units: Player's own discretion
Players will be provided with a standard keyboard and mouse but they can bring their own too.
In any case, organizers decision will be final.

events.description: Clash Royale is a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash of Clans characters and much, much more
events.name: Clash Royale
rules: The tournament will be played under the current Clash Royale tournament level caps.
Any card released fourteen (14) days before the first day of the tournament won't be allowed.

The tournament will use the standard in-game "Tournament" settings for each game: King level cap: 9, Common level cap: 9, Rare level cap: 7, Epic level cap: 4, Legendary level cap: 1, Overtime length: 3min

An official match may only be started and played when a tournament referee has given the signal to start it. Any match started without approval of a referee will be considered as a non-official match.

If a player disconnects in the middle of a battle at any time, the outcome of the battle will stand (i.e: if you reconnect and lose, you lose, if you reconnect and win, you win). If a player suffers a disconnection or more, both players can agree to replay the game, or not.
A best of three match is played in two or three games and is used during the four first round of the loser bracket play-off stage of the tournament.
In case of a draw, the player with the highest total hit points left on his buildings, win.
In case of a perfect draw, same total hit points on both sides, the match has to be played again with the exact same decks.
A best of five match is played in three, four or five games and is used during the play-off stage of the tournament.

In case of a draw, the player with the highest total hit points left on his buildings, win. In case of a perfect draw, same total hit points on both sides, the match has to be played again with the exact same decks.
